com.ephesoft.dcma.kvfinder.data

Class ZonalKeyParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.kvfinder.data.ZonalKeyParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ZonalKeyParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class ZonalKeyParameters holds the information for a key found on the page. It acts as a data carrier for the key. If there is some information added to the key and needs to be passed across various instances, it can be added to this class.

    If N keys are found in a page, N instances of this class will be created.

    Author:
    Ephesoft
